title: Is the Patriots' offense unstoppable?
itunes:title: Is the Patriots' offense unstoppable?
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler break down the latest news in the NFL, including tight end Martellus Bennett being traded to the Patriots and Chip Kelly’s comments on Colin Kaepernick.  Then, the heroes dive into another speed round before ending the show playing a game of Over/Under.
